  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Type 1 DM

          -  Transition to CSII

          -  meeting the costs by health services

          -  sufficient German literacy

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Remission (diabetes duration &lt; 6 months, insulin &lt; 0.5 i.E./kg)

          -  severe learning problems

          -  Investigator's children

          -  Waiting time not advised for medical reasons
      </textblock>
